Askaway is a tool for asking questions behind the veil of anonymity.

==
Current Features

To ask a question the user must provide:
- The question body
- A contact handler like thier
-- Twitter handle
-- Email address
-- Phone number

The askee has to option to  reply publicly or privately. 
- a public reply will show up on their public profile page
- a private reply will only be visible to the person who asked the question


